title: Office Tab Enterprise v11.0.0.228

Office Tab Enterprise v11.0.0.228

Office Tab - Tabbed Browsing, Editing, and Managing of Documents in Microsoft Office 2016, 2013 - 2003 and Office 365

With the standard versions of MicrosoftÂ® Office, you cannot view and edit multiple files within a single tabbed window. Office Tab changes this by introducing a tabbed user interface - as seen in web browsers such as Internet ExplorerÂ® 8, Firefox and Google Chrome - in Microsoft Office 2016, 2013, 2010, 2007, 2003 and Office 365 (Word, ExcelÂ®, PowerPointÂ®, PublisherÂ®, AccessÂ®, Project and VisioÂ®

Open, read, edit, and manage multiple Office documents in a single tabbed window.
Minimize the number of windows you open at the same time.
Save and close all Office documents with one click.
Based on Microsoft Office add-in technology.

New features:
Add the Close Unlocked feature to the right-clicking menu: you can quickly close all unlocked tabs at once in Microsoft Word, Excel or PowerPoint.

Improvements:
1. Update language translations.
2. Improve the installation package.
3. Some minor improvements.

Fixed:
1. Fixed: The Save feature of the right-clicking menu cannot work when only one tab opens in Microsoft Excel 2013 and 2016.
2. Fixed: For the Tabs for Word package, the Close All feature in the right-clicking menu may cause error when there are locked tabs.
